      </CardHeader>
    </Card>
  ))}
</Grid>
```

## Standalone App Structure

### Directory Roles

```
src/
├── components/        ← UI primitives & composites (@ui8kit/core alias)
├── variants/          ← CVA configs (button, badge, card, typography, etc.)
├── lib/               ← utility-props, utils
├── blocks/            ← Page sections (HeroBlock) & page views (*PageView)
├── layouts/           ← MainLayout, AdminLayout
├── partials/          ← Header, Footer, Sidebar, ThemeToggle, DomainNavButton
├── routes/            ← Route components (LandingPage, MenuPage, etc.)
├── providers/         ← theme, AdminAuthContext
├── data/              ← context.ts (createContext, fixtures)
└── css/

fixtures/              ← JSON data (landing, menu, recipes, blog, promotions, admin, shared)
```

### Where to Put New Code — Decision Tree

| Question | Answer | Location |
|----------|--------|----------|
| Is it a layout/content primitive? (Button, Card, Stack, Accordion, Sheet) | Yes | `src/components/` |
| Is it a CVA variant config? | Yes | `src/variants/` |
| Is it a page section or full page view? | Yes | `src/blocks/` |
| Is it a reusable fragment (header, footer, nav)? | Yes | `src/partials/` |
| Is it a page layout wrapper? | Yes | `src/layouts/` |
| Is it a route that loads a PageView? | Yes | `src/routes/` |
| Is it app context or data loading? | Yes | `src/data/` |
| Is it JSON fixture data? | Yes | `fixtures/` |

### Block Types

| Type | Pattern | Examples |
|------|---------|----------|
| Block | Reusable section | `HeroBlock`, `SidebarContent`, `DashSidebar` |
| PageView | Full page composition | `LandingPageView`, `MenuPageView`, `RecipesPageView`, `AdminDashboardPageView` |

**Rule:** Blocks import from `@ui8kit/core` and `@ui8kit/dsl` (If, Var, Loop). No cross-block imports; use partials for shared fragments.

### Cognitive Load — Keep It Simple

1. **Blocks = composition only.** No business logic. Use `Var`, `If`, `Loop` from `@ui8kit/dsl` for data binding.
2. **Data flow:** `fixtures/*.json` → `context.ts` → routes → PageView.
3. **Copy-paste = block + its imports.** When copying a block, you get a self-contained file.
4. **Don't extract "FeatureCard".** Use `Card` from components. Different block types = same Card, different content.

